  // Sub-services translation keys
  d['en']['af.challenges_p_1']='Inability to forecast and manage cash flows effectively threatens operational stability and growth potential.';
  d['en']['af.challenges_h3_2']='Cash Flow Uncertainty';
  d['en']['af.challenges_p_3']='Investors and acquirers require clean, auditable financials. Unreliable records erode confidence and reduce valuation.';
  d['en']['af.challenges_h3_4']='Difficulty Attracting Investment';
  d['en']['af.challenges_p_5']='Manual, fragmented bookkeeping workflows consume valuable resources and increase the risk of errors.';
  d['en']['af.challenges_h3_6']='Inefficient Bookkeeping Processes';
  d['en']['af.challenges_p_7']='Without real-time financial dashboards and analytics, leadership teams operate blind to critical performance indicators.';
  d['en']['af.challenges_h3_8']='Lack of Financial Visibility';
  d['en']['af.challenges_p_9']='Navigating PSAK/IFRS standards, tax regulations, and evolving compliance requirements demands specialized expertise.';
  d['en']['af.challenges_h3_10']='Complex Regulatory Compliance';
  d['en']['af.challenges_p_11']='Poor data quality leads to flawed business decisions, missed opportunities, and increased compliance risk.';
  d['en']['af.challenges_h3_12']='Inaccurate Financial Data';
  d['en']['af.core-services_p_1']='Streamline financial workflows, implement automation, and design scalable processes that reduce costs and improve accuracy.';
  d['en']['af.core-services_h3_2']='Financial Process Optimization';
  d['en']['af.core-services_p_3']='Evaluate and strengthen internal controls, identify process gaps, and ensure governance frameworks meet regulatory expectations.';
  d['en']['af.core-services_h3_4']='Internal Audit &amp; Controls';
  d['en']['af.core-services_p_5']='Custom dashboards, KPI tracking, and management reports that provide actionable insights for informed decision-making.';
  d['en']['af.core-services_h3_6']='Management Reporting &amp; Analytics';
  d['en']['af.core-services_p_7']='Strategic financial leadership for organizations that need executive-level guidance without a full-time CFO commitment.';
  d['en']['af.core-services_h3_8']='CFO Advisory Services';
  d['en']['af.core-services_p_9']='End-to-end bookkeeping, accounts payable/receivable management, and payroll processing with accuracy and efficiency.';
  d['en']['af.core-services_h3_10']='Bookkeeping &amp; Payroll Management';
  d['en']['af.core-services_p_11']='Prepare accurate financial statements compliant with PSAK/IFRS standards. Ensure regulatory filings are timely and error-free.';
  d['en']['af.core-services_h3_12']='Financial Reporting &amp; Compliance';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_1']='Regulatory compliance tracking and reporting checklists';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_2']='Compliance Checklists';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_3']='Actionable steps to optimize financial workflows';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_4']='Process Improvement Recommendations';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_5']='Short and medium-term cash flow projections';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_6']='Cash Flow Forecasts';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_7']='Variance analysis with actionable commentary';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_8']='Budget vs. Actual Analysis';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_9']='Custom KPI dashboards and executive summaries';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_10']='Management Reports &amp; Dashboards';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_11']='Balance sheets, income statements, cash flow statements';
  d['en']['af.deliverables_p_12']='Monthly/Quarterly Financial Statements';
  d['en']['af.experts_p_1']='International Tax · Transfer Pricing';
  d['en']['af.experts_p_2']='Partner, Tax Services';
  d['en']['af.experts_h3_3']='Dyna Agustina';
  d['en']['af.experts_p_4']='M&amp;A · Corporate Advisory';
  d['en']['af.experts_p_5']='Managing Partner';
  d['en']['af.experts_h3_6']='Andi Rio Ilhad Monry';
  d['en']['af.experts_h2_7']='Meet Our Experts';
  d['en']['af.experts_span_8']='Our Team';
  d['en']['af.faq_p_1']='Our Accounting &amp; Finance practice serves clients across manufacturing, technology, energy &amp; resources, healthcare, real estate, and consumer goods industries. Each sector has unique regulatory requirements and reporting needs, and our team brings deep industry-specific expertise to every engagement.';
  d['en']['af.faq_span_2']='What industries does your accounting practice specialize in?';
  d['en']['af.faq_p_3']='Our compliance framework includes regular training on standard updates, systematic review processes, and quality assurance checkpoints at every reporting cycle. We also conduct internal compliance audits to identify and address gaps before they become issues.';
  d['en']['af.faq_span_4']='How does Chatura ensure compliance with PSAK/IFRS requirements?';
  d['en']['af.faq_p_5']='Yes. Our CFO Advisory Services are designed for organizations that need executive-level financial leadership on a flexible basis. We offer part-time CFO, interim CFO, and project-based CFO engagements tailored to your stage of growth and specific requirements.';
  d['en']['af.faq_span_6']='Can Chatura provide part-time or interim CFO services?';
  d['en']['af.faq_p_7']='We prepare financial statements in accordance with Standar Akuntansi Keuangan (SAK), which is based on International Financial Reporting Standards (IFRS). Our team stays current with all PSAK updates and ensures full compliance with OJK and BKPM requirements for listed and private companies alike.';
  d['en']['af.faq_span_8']='What accounting standards does Chatura follow for financial reporting?';
  d['en']['af.solution_span_1']='Process Optimization';
  d['en']['af.solution_span_2']='Real-Time Analytics';
  d['en']['af.solution_span_3']='Strategic CFO Advisory';
  d['en']['af.solution_span_4']='PSAK/IFRS Compliance';
  d['en']['af.solution_p_5']='From establishing robust accounting frameworks and ensuring regulatory compliance to delivering executive-level financial intelligence, we provide the expertise your organization needs to maintain financial integrity and unlock growth opportunities.';
  d['en']['af.solution_p_6']='Our integrated accounting and finance practice combines technical precision with strategic insight. We don\'t just process numbers — we transform financial data into a strategic asset that drives better business decisions.';
  d['en']['af.summary_p_1']='Whether you are a growing enterprise seeking to professionalize your finance function, a listed company navigating regulatory compliance, or an investment-ready organization preparing for due diligence, Chatura delivers the precision, transparency, and strategic guidance your business demands.';
  d['en']['af.summary_p_2']='Our team works closely with CFOs, finance directors, and business owners to streamline accounting processes, strengthen internal controls, and deliver reporting that meets both regulatory requirements and management needs. From day-to-day bookkeeping to complex CFO advisory engagements, we provide the full spectrum of accounting and finance services required to maintain financial integrity and drive sustainable growth.';
  d['en']['af.summary_p_3']='At Chatura Indonesia, our Accounting &amp; Finance practice is built on the principle that accurate, timely financial information is the foundation of every sound business decision. We combine deep technical expertise in Indonesian accounting standards (PSAK) and International Financial Reporting Standards (IFRS) with strategic insight to transform your financial data into a powerful decision-making tool.';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_p_1']='Organizations that have outgrown their initial operating model need structured approaches to scale sustainably.';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_h3_2']='Growth Plateau';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_p_3']='When organizational structure doesn\'t support strategic objectives, execution fails regardless of plan quality.';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_h3_4']='Strategy-Structure Misalignment';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_p_5']='Boards and committees without proper governance frameworks expose organizations to regulatory and reputational risk.';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_h3_6']='Governance Gaps';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_p_7']='Generational changes, founder departures, and executive turnover create uncertainty and risk to business continuity.';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_h3_8']='Leadership Transitions';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_p_9']='Structural misalignment and process gaps limit growth potential and drain resources from core business activities.';
  d['en']['ca.challenges_h3_10']='Organizational Inefficiency';
