  d['en']['ca.faq_p_1']='Yes. We go beyond recommendations to guide implementation, working alongside your team through the transformation process. Our involvement can range from strategic oversight to hands-on project leadership.';
  d['en']['ca.faq_span_2']='Does Chatura provide hands-on implementation support?';
  d['en']['ca.faq_p_3']='Strategic planning engagements typically run 3–6 months. Restructuring and transformation projects may extend to 12+ months depending on scope and complexity. We tailor engagement timelines to your specific needs.';
  d['en']['ca.faq_span_4']='How long do typical advisory engagements last?';
  d['en']['ca.faq_p_5']='Family enterprises are a core focus. We understand the unique dynamics of family businesses — including succession planning, governance structuring, next-generation leadership development, and balancing family interests with business objectives.';
  d['en']['ca.faq_span_6']='Does Chatura work with family-owned businesses?';
  d['en']['ca.faq_p_7']='The right time is when you face a strategic inflection point — growth plateaus, market shifts, leadership transitions, or organizational complexity that internal teams struggle to address independently. Early engagement often prevents larger issues downstream.';
  d['en']['ca.faq_span_8']='When should a company engage corporate advisory services?';
