  d['en']['ca.solution_span_1']='Succession';
  d['en']['ca.solution_span_2']='Governance';
  d['en']['ca.solution_span_3']='Restructuring';
  d['en']['ca.solution_span_4']='Strategic Planning';
  d['en']['ca.solution_p_5']='From strategic planning and corporate restructuring to governance design and succession planning, we provide the objective counsel and hands-on support your organization needs to transform and grow.';
  d['en']['ca.solution_p_6']='Our corporate advisory practice works alongside leadership teams as a trusted strategic partner. We bring external perspective, structured thinking, and deep experience to help you navigate complexity and make better decisions.';
  d['en']['ca.solution_h2_7']='Integrated Corporate Advisory Practice';
  d['en']['ca.solution_span_8']='Our Solution';
  d['en']['ca.summary_p_1']='Whether you are a family enterprise planning generational transition, a listed company undergoing strategic restructuring, or a growing organization seeking to professionalize governance and operations, Chatura provides the objective counsel, structured thinking, and hands-on support your leadership team needs.';
  d['en']['ca.summary_p_2']='Our advisory team brings deep experience across corporate restructuring, governance design, succession planning, and operational improvement. We don\'t deliver generic frameworks — we tailor every engagement to your organization\'s unique context, culture, and strategic objectives.';
  d['en']['ca.summary_p_3']='At Chatura Indonesia, our Corporate Advisory practice is built on the principle that the best strategic decisions come from combining internal leadership insight with external specialist perspective. We work alongside C-suites, boards, and business owners to navigate complexity, manage change, and unlock sustainable growth.';
  d['en']['ca.summary_h2_4']='Advisory as a Catalyst for Transformation';
  d['en']['ca.summary_span_5']='Our Practice';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_p_1']='VAT, customs duties, and other indirect taxes require precise treatment to avoid overpayment or non-compliance.';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_h3_2']='Indirect Tax Complexity';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_p_3']='Without specialized tax planning, businesses often overlook legitimate opportunities to reduce their effective tax rate.';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_h3_4']='Missed Optimization';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_p_5']='International operations create overlapping tax obligations across multiple jurisdictions with different treaty frameworks.';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_h3_6']='Cross-Border Obligations';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_p_7']='Misinterpretation of tax regulations can lead to disputes, penalties, and costly litigation with tax authorities.';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_h3_8']='Tax Dispute Risk';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_p_9']='Multinational operations face stringent transfer pricing documentation requirements and potential double taxation risks.';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_h3_10']='Complex Transfer Pricing';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_p_11']='Frequent changes in Indonesian tax law create compliance risk and require constant monitoring and adaptation.';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_h3_12']='Evolving Tax Regulations';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_h2_13']='Common Tax Challenges We Address';
  d['en']['ts.challenges_span_14']='The Challenge';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_p_1']='Comprehensive VAT planning, customs duty optimization, and indirect tax compliance across all business operations.';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_h3_2']='VAT &amp; Indirect Tax Advisory';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_p_3']='Proactive tax planning strategies to legally minimize tax burden, maximize available incentives, and improve after-tax returns.';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_h3_4']='Tax Planning &amp; Optimization';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_p_5']='Strategic guidance on withholding taxes, tax treaties, repatriation of profits, and cross-border transaction structuring.';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_h3_6']='International Tax &amp; Cross-Border Advisory';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_p_7']='Expert representation in tax disputes, objection proceedings, and litigation support to protect your business interests.';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_h3_8']='Tax Dispute Resolution &amp; Litigation';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_p_9']='Comprehensive transfer pricing documentation, benchmarking studies, and planning to ensure arm\'s-length compliance and minimize double taxation.';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_h3_10']='Transfer Pricing Documentation &amp; Planning';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_p_11']='Accurate preparation and timely filing of corporate income tax returns, monthly VAT returns, and all statutory tax obligations.';
  d['en']['ts.core-services_h3_12']='Corporate Tax Compliance &amp; Filing';
