  d['en']['rm.faq_title']='Frequently Asked Questions';
  d['en']['rm.faq_1_q']='What is enterprise risk management and why does my business need it?';
  d['en']['rm.faq_1_a']='Enterprise risk management (ERM) is a structured approach to identifying, assessing, and responding to risks that could affect your organization\'s objectives. Our practice designs practical frameworks that protect your business while enabling confident, informed growth.';
  d['en']['rm.faq_2_q']='How does Chatura approach internal controls design and testing?';
  d['en']['rm.faq_2_a']='We take a holistic approach that goes beyond checkbox compliance. Our team evaluates your operational processes, maps control gaps, designs tailored control mechanisms, and conducts rigorous testing to ensure effectiveness and regulatory alignment.';
  d['en']['rm.faq_3_q']='Can Chatura assist with fraud investigation and forensic analysis?';
  d['en']['rm.faq_3_a']='Yes. Our forensic team conducts thorough investigations into suspected fraud, financial misconduct, and irregularities. We deliver actionable findings, evidence-based reports, and recommendations to strengthen your anti-fraud posture and support legal proceedings if needed.';
  d['en']['rm.faq_4_q']='Which industries does Chatura\'s risk management practice serve?';
  d['en']['rm.faq_4_a']='We serve a wide range of industries including Financial Services, Manufacturing, Technology, Energy & Resources, Healthcare, and Government & State-Owned Enterprises (SOEs). Our cross-sector experience allows us to tailor risk frameworks to specific regulatory and operational contexts.';
